body_html:
hi @AliceDinh ,thanks for reaching me out
for this tensorflow for poet2: optimize for mobile tutorial I didn't created a folder named libs and copied files in this order:

libs
-libtensorflow_demo.so
-libtensorflow_inference.so
-libandroid_tensorflow_inference_java.jar

because it was not required at all. As per the direction given in the tutorial I only made changes in ClassifierActivity.java file,but due to deprecation warning and tensorflow version problem I made changes in build.gradle script one of the script given in Gradle Scripts.
I hope this explanation might help you in resolving your issue.
Godspeed :)
